N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 111.2 - Eligibility requirements for certification of tree seeds

State Regulations

Certification is limited to those species or species
hybrids for which standards have been established by the State University

College of Forestry seed committee and the certifying agency. Notes
